params._feePercent: is the fee percentage that the marketplace will take from each deal, it can be 0 to 100 (0% to 100%) and can be modified later
params._token: indicates the token that will be used for payments in the marketplace, for production should be PYUSD address, but for fast testing I'm allowing any ERC20 or mock token

params._protocol: is the address of the Protocol contract

createMarketplace(uint8,address).notice: Function to create a new marketplace, callable by anyone

setProtocolAddress(address).notice: Function to set the Protocol contract address, can only be called once and only by the owner
